			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character or move cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move clockwise to release a parasite bomb:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Right Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Reflect attack, grab an enemy, after grabbing the enemy press O repeatedly to beat the cash out of them:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Use characters parasite:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Unleash a parasite bomb:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change characters attribute:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle or R3 Button</font>
